OL,5, Police are investigating former Pink   
OL,6, Floyd bassist Roger Waters after he    
OL,7, wore what appeared to be a Nazi SS     
OL,8, uniform during a concert in Germany.   
OL,10,FPerforming in Berlin on 17 May, Waters 
OL,11,Fwore a long black overcoat with a red  
OL,12,Farmband. He also aimed an imitation    
OL,13,Fmachine gun into the audience.         
OL,15,FGermany bans displaying Nazi symbols - 
OL,16,Fbut the country's laws allow exceptions
OL,17,Ffor artistic or educational reasons.   
OL,19,FWaters said his performance was clearly
OL,20,Fto show "opposition to fascism".       
